# Sandbox secrets. The llm-key.txt file is mounted into the
# container at /run/secrets/llm-key. The binary reads the
# key from this file (path passed via SDD_LLM_API_KEY_FILE).
#
# NEVER commit llm-key.txt. The gitignore below protects
# against accidental commit.
#
# Example: echo "sk-cp-YOUR-KEY" > llm-key.txt && chmod 600 llm-key.txt
